Description: Linked Stage Graph is a Knowledge Graph using a dataset by the Archive of Baden-Wuerttemberg- Germany. It contains black and white photographs and metadata about the Stuttgart State Theaters from the 1890s to the 1940s. The original EAD-XML files were converted to RDF and named entities were extracted and linked to Wikidata and the German Authority Files (GND).
